reviewText: Wow, talk about titles that have little to do with the actual product. This leaves a lot to the imagination. Amy Miller, on the cover, is gorgeous. Some of the girls are very hot, but the overall feel of the DVD is boredom. There is nothing outrageous about this, although, if memory serves me correctly, Danni Ashe does make an appearance here. That alone makes any DVD worthwhile.  But that's it.
